snippet.title: Dinosaur Fossil Hunter — Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
You can now support this game on Kickstarter! https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/playway/dinosaur-fossil-hunter

Add to wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/864700/

Dinosaur Fossil Hunter is a simulator game where you play as paleontologist, exploring desert lands and searching for dinosaur fossil. Search, dig, study uncovered fossils and prepare the skeletons to learn about extinct species and build your own museum!

Follow Pyramid Games for more updates and learn more about our other games!
